"box": [185.06944444444446, 230.3121219135802, 680.0761111111111, 102.61955169753094], "id_box_line": 4, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 230.3121219135802, 680.0761111111111, 14.036805555555588], "text": "Under a series of share repurchase authorizations approved by the Board of Directors, the Company has ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72505, "box": [185.06944444444446, 230.3121219135802, 680.0761111111111, 102.61955169753094], "id_box_line": 5, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 252.45781635802462, 673.8507071759259, 14.036789737654317], "text": "maintained a discretionary buy-back program throughout fiscal 2001. Share repurchases under the repurchase", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72505, "box": [185.06944444444446, 230.3121219135802, 680.0761111111111, 102.61955169753094], "id_box_line": 6, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 274.60351080246915, 673.8847789351852, 14.036789737654317], "text": "program amounted to $7.3 million, $17.6 million and $0.6 million in fiscal 2001, 2000 and 1999, respectively.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72505, "box": [185.06944444444446, 230.3121219135802, 680.0761111111111, 102.61955169753094], "id_box_line": 7, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 296.7491894290123, 673.7296369598765, 14.036805555555588], "text": "As of January 31, 2001, the Company had authorization to repurchase shares up to an additional $4.5 million", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72505, "box": [185.06944444444446, 230.3121219135802, 680.0761111111111, 102.61955169753094], "id_box_line": 8, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 318.8948838734568, 310.0311489197531, 14.036789737654317], "text": "against an aggregate authorization of $30 million.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72506, "box": [185.06944444444446, 341.04057831790124, 673.8463572530865, 58.32816280864199], "id_box_line": 9, "box_line": [213.54166666666666, 341.04057831790124, 645.3699907407408, 14.036789737654317], "text": "During fiscal 1999, the Company repurchased $2.3 million of stock under a 400,000 share repurchase", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72506, "box": [185.06944444444446, 341.04057831790124, 673.8463572530865, 58.32816280864199], "id_box_line": 10, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 363.1862569444444, 673.8463572530865, 14.036805555555588], "text": "program that had been authorized by the Board of Directors in March 1998. This program had been put in", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72506, "box": [185.06944444444446, 341.04057831790124, 673.8463572530865, 58.32816280864199], "id_box_line": 11, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 385.3319513888889, 462.52696334876543, 14.036789737654317], "text": "place to mitigate the dilutive impact of employee compensation programs. ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72507, "box": [185.06941280864197, 451.7627391975308, 680.5074969135801, 191.20231365740744], "id_box_line": 13, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 451.7627391975308, 673.8648958333333, 14.036805555555588], "text": "In June 1998, the Financial Accounting Standards Board issued Statement of Financial Accounting Standards", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72507, "box": [185.06941280864197, 451.7627391975308, 680.5074969135801, 191.20231365740744], "id_box_line": 14, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 473.9084336419753, 680.5074652777777, 14.036789737654317], "text": "(SFAS) No. 133, \u201cAccounting for Derivative Instruments and Hedging Activities,\u201d as amended, which is ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72507, "box": [185.06941280864197, 451.7627391975308, 680.5074969135801, 191.20231365740744], "id_box_line": 15, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 496.0541280864197, 673.8720455246914, 14.036789737654317], "text": "effective for the company as of February 1, 2001. SFAS 133 requires that an entity recognizes all derivatives", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72507, "box": [185.06941280864197, 451.7627391975308, 680.5074969135801, 191.20231365740744], "id_box_line": 16, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 518.199806712963, 673.8620960648149, 14.036805555555588], "text": "as either assets or liabilities measured at fair value. Changes in derivative fair values will either be recognized", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72507, "box": [185.06941280864197, 451.7627391975308, 680.5074969135801, 191.20231365740744], "id_box_line": 17, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 540.3455011574074, 673.8720455246914, 14.036789737654317], "text": "in earnings as offsets to the changes in fair value of related hedged assets, liabilities and firm commitments or,", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72507, "box": [185.06941280864197, 451.7627391975308, 680.5074969135801, 191.20231365740744], "id_box_line": 18, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 562.4911956018518, 673.8648958333333, 14.036789737654317], "text": "for forecasted transactions, deferred and recorded as a component of other stockholders\u2019 equity until the", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72507, "box": [185.06941280864197, 451.7627391975308, 680.5074969135801, 191.20231365740744], "id_box_line": 19, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 584.6368742283951, 673.8549463734568, 14.036805555555588], "text": "hedged transactions occur and are recognized in earnings. The ineffective portion of a hedging derivative\u2019s", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72507, "box": [185.06941280864197, 451.7627391975308, 680.5074969135801, 191.20231365740744], "id_box_line": 20, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 606.7825686728395, 673.648538580247, 14.03678973765426], "text": "change in fair value will be immediately recognized in earnings. Adoption of this statement is not expected to", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72507, "box": [185.06941280864197, 451.7627391975308, 680.5074969135801, 191.20231365740744], "id_box_line": 21, "box_line": [185.06941280864197, 628.9282631172839, 325.55423611111115, 14.03678973765426], "text": "materially impact the Company\u2019s financial statements.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72508, "box": [185.06941280864197, 651.0739417438272, 683.8956439043209, 102.61955169753082], "id_box_line": 22, "box_line": [213.5416350308642, 651.0739417438272, 650.9448043981481, 14.036805555555532], "text": "In December 1999, the Securities and Exchange Commission, \u201cSEC\u201d, issued Staff Accounting Bulletin ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72508, "box": [185.06941280864197, 651.0739417438272, 683.8956439043209, 102.61955169753082], "id_box_line": 23, "box_line": [185.06941280864197, 673.2196361882716, 673.8577777777778, 14.036789737654374], "text": "No. 101, \u201cSAB 101\u201d, \u201cRevenue Recognition in Financial Statements.\u201d SAB 101 summarizes certain of the", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72508, "box": [185.06941280864197, 651.0739417438272, 683.8956439043209, 102.61955169753082], "id_box_line": 24, "box_line": [185.06941280864197, 695.365330632716, 683.8956439043209, 14.036789737654317], "text": "SEC\u2019s views in applying accounting principles generally accepted in the United States to revenue ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72508, "box": [185.06941280864197, 651.0739417438272, 683.8956439043209, 102.61955169753082], "id_box_line": 25, "box_line": [185.06941280864197, 717.5110092592593, 673.8634722222223, 14.036805555555588], "text": "recognition in financial statements. The Company adopted the guidence of this bulletin during fiscal 2001,", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72508, "box": [185.06941280864197, 651.0739417438272, 683.8956439043209, 102.61955169753082], "id_box_line": 26, "box_line": [185.06941280864197, 739.6567037037037, 472.1278441358025, 14.036789737654317], "text": "which had no material impact on the Company\u2019s revenue recognition policy.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Sabon-Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 72509, "box": [185.06944444444446, 806.0837268518519, 574.5267044753086, 14.036805555555532], "id_box_line": 28, "box_line": [185.06944444444446, 806.0837268518519, 574.526704